<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 22:07:46 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>乌克兰外交官：内塔尼亚胡在与泽连斯基的通话中称赞乌克兰防空</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/ukrainian-diplomat-netanyahu-lauded-ukrainian-air-defense-in-call-with-zelenskyy/00000191-9a8f-d396-a59d-ffdfdc140000</link><description>泽伦斯基发言人表示，在两国领导人自十月以来的首次通话中，以色列总理“表达了对乌克兰主权和领土完整的支持”</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 20:38:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/ukrainian-diplomat-netanyahu-lauded-ukrainian-air-defense-in-call-with-zelenskyy/00000191-9a8f-d396-a59d-ffdfdc140000</guid></item><item><title>美国会因为本-格维尔和斯莫特里奇试图点燃中东而制裁他们吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-28/ty-article/.highlight/will-the-u-s-hold-ben-gvir-smotrich-accountable-for-trying-to-set-the-mideast-on-fire/00000191-9a0e-d290-a5b3-fe9e8c690000</link><description>新一轮制裁，加上针对极右翼以色列部长的日益敌对的公开言论，表明本-格维尔和斯莫特里奇仍然是旨在避免中东进一步危机的美国官员心目中的首要人物</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 19:48:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-28/ty-article/.highlight/will-the-u-s-hold-ben-gvir-smotrich-accountable-for-trying-to-set-the-mideast-on-fire/00000191-9a0e-d290-a5b3-fe9e8c690000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军宣布，10 月 7 日被杀并被带到加沙的士兵尸体已返回以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/body-of-soldier-killed-on-october-7-and-taken-to-gaza-returned-to-israel-idf-announces/00000191-9a2d-df2d-a3bd-babdc0e40000</link><description>根据家人的要求，遗体被送回以色列的阵亡士兵的身份尚未公布</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 19:09:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/body-of-soldier-killed-on-october-7-and-taken-to-gaza-returned-to-israel-idf-announces/00000191-9a2d-df2d-a3bd-babdc0e40000</guid></item><item><title>“生命的价值正在崩溃”：抗议车队驶往加沙呼吁达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/value-of-life-is-crumbling-protest-convoy-drives-to-gaza-calling-for-a-hostage-deal/00000191-9a0a-dffe-a9b7-db3af4ae0000</link><description>以色列人质家属在特拉维夫集会，然后随车队前往贝埃里基布兹，在那里他们猛烈抨击内塔尼亚胡坚持加沙边界问题，破坏了人质协议谈判。失去亲人的母亲说：“我很抱歉，费城路线比人质更重要”</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 18:58:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/value-of-life-is-crumbling-protest-convoy-drives-to-gaza-calling-for-a-hostage-deal/00000191-9a0a-dffe-a9b7-db3af4ae0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队调查发现定居者对巴勒斯坦村庄的袭击是“恐怖行为”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-probe-finds-settler-attack-on-palestinian-village-a-terrorist-act/00000191-99ce-d975-a9f3-bfffdff90000</link><description>中央司令部司令说：“这是以色列人发动的最严重的恐怖袭击，我们因没有更早到达并保护他们而失败”</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 17:42:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-probe-finds-settler-attack-on-palestinian-village-a-terrorist-act/00000191-99ce-d975-a9f3-bfffdff90000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日遇难者家属不允许在国家仪式上“愤世嫉俗地使用”他们的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/ex-hostages-oct-7-victims-families-deny-cynical-use-of-loved-ones-names-for-ceremony/00000191-9959-d222-a797-9f5f56d70000</link><description>他们要求不要提及他们亲人的名字，也不要“以任何身份”展示他们的照片。内塔尼亚胡的一位盟友告诉媒体，总理的“仇恨者”想要一个“替代国家”，仪式的领导人、交通部长米里·雷格夫表示，尽管有“噪音”，她仍将继续前进</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 17:09:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/ex-hostages-oct-7-victims-families-deny-cynical-use-of-loved-ones-names-for-ceremony/00000191-9959-d222-a797-9f5f56d70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第327天：美国制裁西岸激进定居点的安全负责人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-327-u-s-sanctions-security-chief-of-radical-west-bank-settlement/00000191-99d8-dffe-a9b7-dbfaa0180001</link><description>以色列代表团启程前往卡塔尔继续停火谈判，一位消息人士称，如果费城走廊和拉法过境点没有灵活性，“我们能否确保人质获释值得怀疑” ■ 以色列国防军公布对定居者的调查结果本月早些时候发生的骚乱导致一名巴勒斯坦人死亡，以色列国防军称，警方从辛贝特那里获得了情报，应该采取行动 ■ 这是战争开始 327 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 16:43:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-327-u-s-sanctions-security-chief-of-radical-west-bank-settlement/00000191-99d8-dffe-a9b7-dbfaa0180001</guid></item><item><title>从哈马斯囚禁中获救的以色列人质回家庆祝他小儿子的一岁生日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-rescued-from-hamas-captivity-is-home-for-his-youngest-sons-first-birthday/00000191-989e-d222-a797-9e9fc2ac0000</link><description>以色列国防军部队在一个地下大院进行搜查后，人们普遍怀疑哈马斯人质可能就藏在那里，凯德·法尔汉·卡迪被单独找到。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 14:45:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-rescued-from-hamas-captivity-is-home-for-his-youngest-sons-first-birthday/00000191-989e-d222-a797-9e9fc2ac0000</guid></item><item><title>“生活就像地狱”：约旦河西岸旅游之都伯利恒变成鬼城</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/life-has-been-hell-inside-bethlehem-the-west-banks-tourism-capital-turned-ghost-town/00000191-97e9-d13a-ab93-dfff37850000</link><description>巴勒斯坦城市伯利恒每年都会接待多达 150 万名游客。以色列-加沙战争对其造成了毁灭性影响，游客纷纷远离，出租车司机称他们平均每天的收入相当于一包香烟</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 14:32:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/life-has-been-hell-inside-bethlehem-the-west-banks-tourism-capital-turned-ghost-town/00000191-97e9-d13a-ab93-dfff37850000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列士兵在加沙地带战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-combat/00000191-9862-df0a-ab9f-f96b0c550000</link><description>中士阿米特·弗里德曼 (Amit Friedman)，19 岁，军士长。 （res.）Yohay Hay Glam，32 岁，分别于周二和周三被杀。根据以色列国防军记录，自战争爆发以来已有 704 名士兵阵亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 14:32:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-combat/00000191-9862-df0a-ab9f-f96b0c550000</guid></item><item><title>无视高等法院和总检察长，以色列正在加速走向宪法危机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-is-racing-toward-a-constitutional-crisis/00000191-9473-df0a-ab9f-f57ba50a0000</link><description>以色列政府无视高等法院的裁决并不是什么新鲜事，但专家表示，这种趋势近年来有愈演愈烈的趋势。与此同时，部长们一再拒绝接受总检察长具有约束力的意见，并对她公开敌视，这是前所未有的</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 13:47:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-is-racing-toward-a-constitutional-crisis/00000191-9473-df0a-ab9f-f57ba50a0000</guid></item><item><title>卖淫不是一种选择，语言应该反映出这一点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/prostitution-isnt-a-choice-and-language-should-reflect-that/00000191-98c2-db54-a7d3-d9c346fc0000</link><description>以色列的一项新举措提供了一个词汇，帮助媒体更道德地报道卖淫，将焦点转移到皮条客和嫖客的活动上</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 12:24:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/prostitution-isnt-a-choice-and-language-should-reflect-that/00000191-98c2-db54-a7d3-d9c346fc0000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷圣殿山/阿克萨圣殿的“现状”是什么？为什么如此不稳定？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/haaretz-explains/2024-08-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-is-the-status-quo-at-jerusalems-temple-mount-al-aqsa-and-why-is-it-so-precarious/00000191-94d5-d13a-ab93-dcf75dfd0000</link><description>圣殿山/阿克萨大院是犹太教和穆斯林圣地的所在地，得益于自 1967 年以来一直保持不变的政策，圣殿山/阿克萨大院保持了两种宗教之间脆弱的和平。极右翼部长本-格维尔一直表示以色列的政策已经改变。这会产生什么影响？国土报解释</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 10:56:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/haaretz-explains/2024-08-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-is-the-status-quo-at-jerusalems-temple-mount-al-aqsa-and-why-is-it-so-precarious/00000191-94d5-d13a-ab93-dcf75dfd0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人报告以色列军队在约旦河西岸的袭击中造成九人死亡、八人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/palestinians-report-nine-killed-eight-wounded-in-israeli-army-west-bank-raids/00000191-97e9-df0a-ab9f-f7e97b7d0000</link><description>以色列军队同时开展了两项反恐行动，使用无人机并限制进入医院。以色列外交部长将此次袭击比作加沙行动，称以色列应考虑“在约旦河西岸临时撤离”</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 09:24:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/palestinians-report-nine-killed-eight-wounded-in-israeli-army-west-bank-raids/00000191-97e9-df0a-ab9f-f7e97b7d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列团队前往卡塔尔参加加沙谈判；资料来源：“除非内塔尼亚胡灵活，否则不会达成协议”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-delegation-heads-to-qatar-for-gaza-cease-fire-talks/00000191-9666-dd8c-addd-bff6357d0000</link><description>以色列派遣代表团这一事实表明各方都致力于这一进程，但以色列消息人士称，内塔尼亚胡的“红线问题”——费城路线和拉法过境点——没有取得进展</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 03:02:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-delegation-heads-to-qatar-for-gaza-cease-fire-talks/00000191-9666-dd8c-addd-bff6357d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军宣布，10 月 7 日被杀并被带到加沙的士兵尸体已返回以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article-live/israel-launches-counterterror-op-in-west-bank-palestinians-say-at-least-four-killed/00000191-96c7-d13a-ab93-def775cb0000</link><description>美国制裁约旦河西岸定居点安全负责人、定居者组织 ■ 以色列国防军称其在叙利亚和黎巴嫩边境杀害了伊斯兰圣战组织高级成员 ■ 人质家属在特拉维夫集会寻求达成协议 ■ 以色列士兵在加沙中部战斗中丧生 ■ 以色列国防军调查称军队“没有采取足够的措施来制止吉特的定居者骚乱</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 02:29:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article-live/israel-launches-counterterror-op-in-west-bank-palestinians-say-at-least-four-killed/00000191-96c7-d13a-ab93-def775cb0000</guid></item><item><title>担心伊朗报复袭击，美国在该地区保留两艘航母</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/concerned-about-iranian-revenge-attack-u-s-keeps-two-aircraft-carriers-in-region/00000191-953f-d302-add5-9fbf55cd0000</link><description>在真主党周日的袭击遭到挫败后，拜登政府仍然担心伊朗对德黑兰伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚遇刺事件的反应，并加强了在该地区的海军和空中舰队的部署，同时向以色列紧急运送武器</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 22:30:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/concerned-about-iranian-revenge-attack-u-s-keeps-two-aircraft-carriers-in-region/00000191-953f-d302-add5-9fbf55cd0000</guid></item><item><title>雷格夫驳斥批评，拒绝改变以色列10月7日纪念仪式计划的呼吁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/regev-rejects-calls-to-change-israels-plans-for-october-7-memorial-ceremony/00000191-9500-d13a-ab93-ddb731300000</link><description>交通部长表示，计划中的仪式没有任何改变，仪式将在没有观众的情况下现场直播，并包括预先录制的视频</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 20:46:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/regev-rejects-calls-to-change-israels-plans-for-october-7-memorial-ceremony/00000191-9500-d13a-ab93-ddb731300000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部门规划圣殿山导游服务；国家安全委员会尚未回应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministry-planning-temple-mount-tours-national-security-council-yet-to-respond/00000191-9538-d60a-a395-bdbd6da50000</link><description>以色列遗产部表示，参观的内容将受到监控，以避免“为了推进反犹太议程而编写的另类事实和巴勒斯坦叙述”。总理办公室证实国家安全委员会尚未批准该倡议</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 20:13:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministry-planning-temple-mount-tours-national-security-council-yet-to-respond/00000191-9538-d60a-a395-bdbd6da50000</guid></item><item><title>发育不良、失败、可怕：内塔尼亚胡政府纪念 10 月 7 日周年纪念的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-27/ty-article/.highlight/stunted-failed-horrifying-the-netanyahu-governments-plan-to-mark-october-7-anniversary/00000191-9480-dd8c-addd-bdf4ddce0000</link><description>交通部长米里·雷格夫正在推进的 10 月 7 日国家仪式将完美地体现内塔尼亚胡政府对当天遭受最大损失的人们的不受欢迎、情绪低落的行为和失败</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 19:04:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-27/ty-article/.highlight/stunted-failed-horrifying-the-netanyahu-governments-plan-to-mark-october-7-anniversary/00000191-9480-dd8c-addd-bdf4ddce0000</guid></item></channel></rss>